   "source": [
    "#  Spaceship Titanic - ML Project\n",
    "\n",
    "## Files Description\n",
    "\n",
    "| File | Description |\n",
    "|------|------------|\n",
    "| **train.csv** | Personal records for about two-thirds (~8700) of the passengers, used as training data. |\n",
    "| **test.csv** | Personal records for the remaining one-third (~4300) of the passengers, used as test data. Your task is to predict `Transported`. |\n",
    "| **sample_submission.csv** | Submission file in correct format containing `PassengerId` and predicted `Transported` values (`True` or `False`). |\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Field Descriptions (train.csv)\n",
    "\n",
    "| Column | Description | Possible Values / Notes |\n",
    "|--------|------------|------------------------|\n",
    "| PassengerId | Unique Id for each passenger | Format: `gggg_pp` (`gggg`=group, `pp`=number within group) |\n",
    "| HomePlanet | Planet the passenger departed from | e.g., Earth, Mars, Europa |\n",
    "| CryoSleep | Whether passenger is in suspended animation | `True` / `False` |\n",
    "| Cabin | Cabin number where the passenger is staying | Format: `deck/num/side` (`side`=P for Port, S for Starboard) |\n",
    "| Destination | Planet the passenger will be debarking to | e.g., TRAPPIST-1e, PSO J318.5-22, 55 Cancri e |\n",
    "| Age | Age of the passenger | Numeric |\n",
    "| VIP | Whether the passenger paid for VIP service | `True` / `False` |\n",
    "| RoomService | Amount billed at Room Service | Numeric |\n",
    "| FoodCourt | Amount billed at Food Court | Numeric |\n",
    "| ShoppingMall | Amount billed at Shopping Mall | Numeric |\n",
    "| Spa | Amount billed at Spa | Numeric |\n",
    "| VRDeck | Amount billed at VR Deck | Numeric |\n",
    "| Name | First and last names of the passenger | Text |\n",
    "| Transported | Whether passenger was transported to another dimension (target) | `True` / `False` |\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "## 📝 Goal\n",
    "- Bulid a model to predict whether each passenger was **Transportted** after the spaceship accident.\n",
    "- My goal for now is to **practice the full ML pipeline**: EDA → Preprocessing → Modeling → Submission\n",
    "\n",
    "## 📂 Files Used\n",
    "- `train.csv` → Training data with Target (`Transported`)  \n",
    "- `test.csv` → Test data without Target  \n",
    "- `sample_submission.csv` → Format required for Kaggle submission\n",
    "\n",
    "## \n",
    "\n",
    "## 🔹 Planned Steps\n",
    "1. Load and explore the data (EDA)  \n",
    "2. Clean the data and handle missing values  \n",
    "3. Feature Engineering  \n",
    "4. Build the first model (Logistic Regression / Random Forest)  \n",
    "5. Evaluate the model on a validation set  \n",
    "6. Generate the Submission file and upload to Kaggle  \n",
    "7. Gradually improve the model and experiment with additional Feature Engineering\n"
   ]
  },
